newuser@LAPTOP-MLPJMQD2:~/pectra$  GOCACHE=$(pwd)/.gocache go run prysm_blob_schedule_poc.go
[legacy] succeeded: main.beaconConfig{BlobSchedule:[]main.blobScheduleEntry{main.blobScheduleEntry{Epoch:"1024", MaxBlobsPerBlock:"18"}}}
