 at java.base/java.util.OptionalInt.orElseThrow(OptionalInt.java:247)
 at org.hyperledger.besu.config.BlobSchedule.create(BlobSchedule.java:49)
 at org.hyperledger.besu.config.BlobScheduleTest.create_fromObjectNode_parsesFields(BlobScheduleTest.java:17)
...

```

