### Mitigation

As with the other nodes, update the sampling size for DA, only when we have subscribed to the subnets already and have peers for them already. Could use effective epoch/slot approach.

`handle_data_columns_by_range_request_inner` filters `req.columns` against `custody_columns_for_epoch(Some(start_epoch))` a single time, so any column whose custody assignment begins later in the requested range is silently dropped before lookup/response.

```rust
