        // Simulate the heartbeat custody path (tests in this module can call private fns).
        pm.maintain_custody_peers();

        // AFTER custody maintenance, discovery should be requested for the new subnets.
        //as explained queuing with this delay, after we already check the slot 1 of epoch N+1's Data
        //availability is critical for consensus and block importing, because DA check could fail
        //Discovery may take up to 60 seconds to find proper peers. Depending on the network conditions.
        assert!(
            pm.events.iter().any(|e| matches!(e, PeerManagerEvent::DiscoverSubnetPeers(v) if !v.is_empty())),
